      <title>第六街和姆努钦将以 51 亿美元收购保险公司 Enstar</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/sixth-street-and-mnuchin-to-buy-insurer-enstar-for-5-1-billion</link>
