      <title>美国寻求切断与中国的联系，药明康德销售额下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/wuxi-apptec-sees-sales-drop-as-us-seeks-to-cut-ties-with-china</link>
